{"tid":2415052,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"散戶輸錢既pattern","createTime":"2021-02-20T02:59:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T09:03:18.000Z","uid":293494,"like":220,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2e02299538f709b85f43fae6b8b5415b5fb24d4b","tid":2415052,"uid":293494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T02:59:17.000Z","msg":"1. 見有隻股不斷升：<br />\n<br />\n唔敢入<br />\n<br />\n2. 全連登唱好：<br />\n<br />\n都係唔敢入，但係有D心動<br />\n<br />\n3. 隻股再不斷升：<br />\n<br />\n以為係百倍股 ，驚唔買就執輸無錢賺，all in 高位接貨<br />\n<br />\n4. 隻股高位回10%：<br />\n<br />\nSH，怕係震倉<br />\n<br />\n5. 隻股高位回20%：<br />\n<br />\n唔敢放，全連登唱好，話「信念！SH！」<br />\n<br />\n6. 隻股高位回40%：<br />\n<br />\n驚輸身家，同自己講「止蝕！攞返六成本金，再買其他股賺返蝕左嘅返黎！」跟住低位放曬貨，安心訓教。<br />\n<br />\n7. 第二日醒返，收市前隻股係低位反彈，升返10%：<br />\n<br />\n「好快就跌返姐，D 散戶仲接貨，蝕死佢地啊。」<br />\n<br />\n8. 一個星期後隻股升穿最高位，不斷向上：<br />\n<br />\n「點解會咁？無理由既！！！睇你升得幾耐」<br />\n<br />\n9. 兩個星期後隻股依然不斷大升：<br />\n<br />\n以為係百倍股 ，驚唔買就執輸無錢賺，all in 再高位接貨<br />\n<br />\n10. repeat no.4-9，再返工對冲，跟住計一計數，發覺已經蝕左層首期"},{"pid":"36f7a911bc074de35f40d59bc0687cb88376ba66","tid":2415052,"uid":60563,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:01:52.000Z","msg":"高買低賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b34f16b4b36e725ad03d9e83fffe5c5e29111c40","tid":2415052,"uid":5770,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:02:03.000Z","msg":"事實係識好多人買股都好驚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不如買arkk"},{"pid":"fdadfef4b55f913abba400f4e80d1c3fffe19759","tid":2415052,"uid":218865,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:08:11.000Z","msg":"所以講到尾就係要一買就del app"},{"pid":"4b98194db6db1c48b80fabe3ecd5d151bab965cd","tid":2415052,"uid":79869,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:09:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/08/27/2741784-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fat